      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Russian (Arts)              : The Russian twentieth-century literary dynamic up to the watershed of Stalin's death (1953). Carving out cultural territory against ideological polemics, revolutionary versus traditional values, the explosion of avant-garde experimentation under mounting critical conformism as reflected in major works and authors (Mayakovsky, Babel, Bulgakov, Platonov and others).          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
