      English (Arts)              : Study of a particular theme or genre of significance to the development of medieval literature.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Fall 2014          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
      Instructors:                        Michael Van Dussen (Fall)                  </p>

    
